<TEXT>
<P>
   FOR THE LOVE OF MARS
</P>
<P>
   FIRST AMERICANS: ORIGINS OF MAN
</P>
<P>
   These are stories that clients of DISCOVER NEWS SERVICE recently
received.
</P>
<P>
   DISCOVER NEWS SERVICE, which is available through The New York
Times Syndicate, captures all the wonders of discovery in the
