<P>
   COXNET- FOOD 0305 _ You see the description on the menu _
caramelized _ and in an instant, you're a kid again on the midway
at the county fair. That little taste of the sweet tinged with fire
is being touted on more and more restaurant menus these days, so
much so that Food &AMP; Wine magazine spotted caramelizing as a top
menu trend for 1999. (Walker, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   WITH
</P>
<P>
   CYBERSPICE _ Lack of time, energy or extended family to pitch in
no longer is a valid rationalization for not putting together a
family meal at least a couple of times a week _ not with the
Internet standing ready to provide help for time-starved cooks.
(Parham, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
