<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-10 13:21 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4935 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BOX-HOLYFIELD-BOS &LR;      03-10 1338
