<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-10 13:52 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4994 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SKILLED-FOREIGNERS-2T     03-10 1155
