<P>
   MCNAMARA-COLUMN (Undated) _ After all this time, all the
judicial proceedings, all of Louise Woodward's appeals exhausted,
and yet, incredibly, it is still Deborah and Sunil Eappen who
remain on trial. By Eileen McNamara.
