<HEADLINE>


</HEADLINE>
 
(For use by NYTimes News Service clients)  
(Budget being resent with slug change) The Los Angeles Daily News plans to move the following stories for
use by NYTimes News Service clients. They will move in the ``e''
entertainment news file. For questions, contact Bob McCarthy at
(818) 713-3665. 
 
 
PFEIFFER-DEEP (Los Angeles) _ Michelle Pfeiffer bought the movie
rights to Jacquelyn Mitchard's novel ``The Deep End of the Ocean''
before it was ever published. ``I couldn't put it down, and then I
had to put it down, if you know what I mean,'' says the
actress-producer and a mother herself. By Bob Strauss. 
 
 

