Republican presidential campaign on the same footing as her chief
competition in the early running for the 2000 nomination,
announcing that she is launching an exploratory committee that can
raise and spend money. Gov. George W. Bush of Texas named his
exploratory committee on Sunday. By ALAN BERNSTEIN. (Already
filed.)
