endorses a bill that would lower the legal amount of alcohol that
drivers could have in their body from 0.10 percent to 0.08 percent.
The bill is endorsed by Gov. George W. Bush and Mothers Against
Drunk Driving. By JAIME STOCKWELL. (Already filed.)
