   BKN-SONICS (Milwaukee) _ The Seattle SuperSonics face their
former coach, George Karl, when they play the Milwaukee Bucks.
</P>
<P>
   By Ronald Tillery. (Story will move in ``s'' category.)
</P>
<P>
   BBA-MARINERS (Peoria, Ariz.) _ The Mariners' Jay Buhner returns
