<P>
   EDITORS: Please note the change in the naming of our graphic
files. The story's keyword will be separated from the graphic's
slug name with an underscore ``_'' instead of a slash ``/''.
</P>
<P>
   Example: KOSOVO_locator map.sit
</P>
<P>
   The change is immediate. This should not effect your ability to
do a keyword search for graphics on the AP, Newscom, Presslink or
Wieck. If you are encountering problems or you have questions,
please contact the New York Times Graphic Service at (888) 603-1036
or (212)556-4204.
</P>
