<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-10 22:25 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5774 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BBO-ANDERSON-COLUMN-N     03-10 0839
